OL,3,C'Don't regulate flexible work out of
OL,4,Cexistence', retail industry warns
OL,6,FThe Government should not regulate
OL,7,Fflexible jobs "out of existence" with
OL,8,Freforms which will scrap zero-hours
OL,9,Fcontracts, retail industry leaders
OL,10,Fhave warned.
OL,12,FLast week, ministers laid out details
OL,13,Ffor proposals which could ensure
OL,14,Fguaranteed hours for workers.
OL,16,FIt started a consultation over
OL,17,Fpotential new rules which would
OL,18,Frequire employers to offer staff on
OL,19,Fzero hours or short hours contracts a
OL,20,Fminimum number of hours each week on
OL,21,Fregular working hours.
OL,26,@oD@OOUoD@`O]
