CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780812268
OL,3,C'Don't regulate flexible work out of
OL,4,Cexistence', retail industry warns
OL,6,FThe consultation on how to implement
OL,7,Fthe changes, which are due to come
OL,8,Finto effect next year, flagged that
OL,9,Fthe Government would prefer workers to
OL,10,Fbe guaranteed a minimum of between
OL,11,Feight and 20 hours per week, if
OL,12,Fcurrent contracts are at or below that
OL,13,Flevel.
OL,15,FHowever, the move has come under fire
OL,16,Ffrom unions, employers and trade
OL,17,Fgroups.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
