OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780812268
OL,3,C'Don't regulate flexible work out of
OL,4,Cexistence', retail industry warns
OL,6,FOn Sunday, the British Retail
OL,7,FConsortium (BRC) said the proposed
OL,8,Freforms are "poorly designed" and
OL,9,Fwould put opportunities for many
OL,10,Fworkers at risk.
OL,12,FPolling commissioned by the
OL,13,Forganisation found that two-thirds
OL,14,F(67%) of part-time workers took their
OL,15,Frole because they needed flexibility
OL,16,Faround commitments such as study,
OL,17,Fchildcare and caring responsibilities.
OL,19,FThe BRC also highlighted more than
OL,20,Fhalf of all retail jobs (57.8%) are
OL,21,Fpart-time.
OL,26,@pD@MOUpD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
