OL,3,C'Don't regulate flexible work out of
OL,4,Cexistence', retail industry warns
OL,6,FThe Guaranteed Hours consultation
OL,7,Fcomes shortly after the Milburn Review
OL,8,Fhighlighted the scale of the challenge
OL,9,Ffacing youth employment, with more
OL,10,Fthan one million young people aged 16
OL,11,Fto 24 not in education, employment or
OL,12,Ftraining.
OL,14,FHelen Dickinson, chief executive of
OL,15,Fthe BRC, said: "It's vital that we
OL,16,Fdon't regulate flexible jobs out of
OL,17,Fexistence.
OL,26,@wD@POU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
