PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780812268
OL,3,C'Don't regulate flexible work out of
OL,4,Cexistence', retail industry warns
OL,6,F"Flexible and part-time work is how
OL,7,Fmillions of people make employment
OL,8,Fwork for them ` balancing shifts
OL,9,Falongside study, childcare or caring
OL,10,Fresponsibilities, and retail plays a
OL,11,Fvital role in providing those
OL,12,Fopportunities.
OL,14,F"For many workers, that flexibility
OL,15,Fisn't (just) nice to have ` it's what
OL,16,Fmakes employment possible and allows
OL,17,Fthem to take on extra hours when it
OL,18,Fsuits them.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
