OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780812268
OL,3,C'Don't regulate flexible work out of
OL,4,Cexistence', retail industry warns
OL,6,F"Retailers need to offer those
OL,7,Fadditional hours when demand is there,
OL,8,Fbut they cannot guarantee them all-
OL,9,Fyear round."
OL,11,FA Department for Business and Trade
OL,12,Fspokesperson said: "Reducing
OL,13,Funcertainty over hours and pay will
OL,14,Fboost living standards for millions of
OL,15,Fworkers, benefit businesses and
OL,16,Fsupport economic growth.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@LO]tD@TOU
