OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780812268
OL,3,C'Don't regulate flexible work out of
OL,4,Cexistence', retail industry warns
OL,6,F"Those offered guaranteed hours will
OL,7,Fbe able to turn them down and remain
OL,8,Fon their current arrangement if they
OL,9,Fwish, and employers and workers can
OL,10,Fexpress their views on what the impact
OL,11,Fof different options could be by
OL,12,Fresponding to the consultation."
